videos.headline: Highlight: Manning racks up five TDs as No. 2 Texas routs UTSA
videos.description: Arch Manning comes in for the injured Quinn Ewers at quarterback and produces five touchdowns for the Longhorns in a 56-7 rout of the Roadrunners.
